<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t16910115-22">
               <interp inst="t16910115-22" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t16910115-22" type="year" value="1691"></interp>
               <interp inst="t16910115-22" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/16910115"></interp>
               <interp inst="t16910115-22" type="date" value="16910115"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t16910115-22-off95-c93" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910115-22-defend93 t16910115-22-off95 t16910115-22-verdict98"></join>
         
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t16910115-22-defend93" type="defendantName">
                  Christopher 
                  Pearse
               <interp inst="t16910115-22-defend93" type="surname" value="Pearse"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-defend93" type="given" value="Christopher"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-defend93" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , was Tryed for a <rs id="t16910115-22-off95" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-off95" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-off95" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               Robbery in the High-way, together with 
                     <persName id="t16910115-22-person94">Tho. Cox</persName>
                   since Executed, on the <rs id="t16910115-22-cd96" type="crimeDate">23d of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910115-22-off95 t16910115-22-cd96"></join> last
            </rs>. It was made appear thus, viz. That the Prisoner and another Man met one 
               <persName id="t16910115-22-victim95" type="victimName">
                  Bowcher
               <interp inst="t16910115-22-victim95" type="surname" value="Bowcher"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-victim95" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910115-22-off95 t16910115-22-victim95"></join>
                  </persName>
             in <placeName id="t16910115-22-crimeloc97">Honslow-Hearth</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t16910115-22-crimeloc97" type="placeName" value="Honslow-Hearth"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t16910115-22-crimeloc97" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910115-22-off95 t16910115-22-crimeloc97"></join>, and pulled him off his Mare by the Hair of his Head, and took away the Mare, price 7 l. and a piece of Gold, and two Gold Rings; which Mare (being put into the Gazette) was found after in the Prisoners Stable. The Prisoner denyed it, and said that he was none of the Man, and called some Witnesses to prove it; one of which said, That the Prisoner was with him and several others at an Execution at Tyburn, the same day that the Robbery was committed; yet the Evidence for the King constantly affirming their former Depositions, he was found <rs id="t16910115-22-verdict98" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-verdict98" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs> of the Robbery.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t16910115-22-punish99" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16910115-22-punish99" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910115-22-defend93 t16910115-22-punish99"></join>
               
                     <note>[Death. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
